úóŔ^archive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-08-23-two-years-of-nushell.mdŔ@24ea6b9cadabdcd880b6122583801441f908af66b2f7b8e91d7c77c2a053e88eĽtitle: Two years of NushellĎīTwo years of Nushellŕ



Stock cake photo with a 2
Happy birthday, Nushell!
Happy birthday, Nushell! Today marks the second year for Nushell since its first public release. We wanted to write a bit about what the last year has meant and share some of the highlights and lowlights along the way.
